Class Server

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.googlecode.jmxtrans.model.Server
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JmxConnectionProvider

    @Immutable
 @ThreadSafe
public class Server
extends Object
implements JmxConnectionProvider
    Represents a jmx server that we want to connect to. This also stores the queries that we want to execute against the server.
